On your birthday dearest brother, I look back and cherish all the beautiful time we have spent together and created amazing life-lasting memories. 
The joys we have shared together, sorrows we have faced; the knees we scraped while climbing those walls hehe and the laughs we had living the life we lived.. People often say that we look twin brother sister hehe which you often say you feel lucky about (wink wink). 
I cherish all our funny secrets, I truly am lucky to be able to share my secrets with my brother as my best friend. We played and fought specially over Sachin and SRK or badminton and cricket, cried and laughed, danced and sung specially the games we used to play with Popo hehe (you hardly got it right) but now I know you are better at it, lol.. Happy? frowned and smiled, shared family foes and secrets, did stupidly crazy things together specially with our partner in crime Preety, teased each other and our beautiful elder sister (which we loved doing it and still do), the times when you team up with Prince and tease me and all the crazy things and jokes you guys get upto, but most importantly always being each other's pillar of support in times of need. 
We want to thank you for being such a great brother and more a friend. Thanks for all your support, love, care and affection. You are someone I can count on always and you have always been there for me in all my ups and downs. I just can't believe that you are grown up now and give me lectures and teachings of life and wisdom. Hehe as in my eyes you have always been my little brother who makes me proud ó¾µ
As we wish you the best birthday ever, it brings a smile on our face to see that we have yet another eternity to make tons of such fond memories together. 
A brother is a friend that God gives us, a Friend is a brother our heart choose for.. We are really proud of you. 
 Love you Bhai â¤ï¸
We wish you long life, full of fun and fulfilment.
